"text": "exposure to foreign currency risk. The contract obligates the Company to purchase a total of Ps. 853.0 million at an exchange", "bbox": [85.5, 981.2, 1136.1, 1004.3]}, {"text": "rate of Ps. 13.12 to each U.S. dollar with a maturity date of December 31, 2013. The Company has not designated this forward", "bbox": [85.5, 1006.2, 1146.0, 1029.3]}, {"text": "contract as a hedging instrument for hedge accounting purposes. The Company will mark the contract to market at the end of", "bbox": [85.5, 1031.2, 1132.7, 1054.3]}, {"text": "each reporting period and recognize any foreign exchange gain or loss within the consolidated statements of income.", "bbox": [85.5, 1056.2, 1058.4, 1079.3]}]}